    (19,'Rattata',30,56,35,'Normal','NA','Run Away','Guts','Hustle','3.5 kG','Purple','Neutral','NA','Criticized as a "filthy rodent" by GamesRadar and "rubbish" by the Official Nintendo Magazine. Its teeth grow very long over time, so it has to gnaw on logs, houses, telephone poles and more so it can be quite a pest at times.','https://img.pokemondb.net/sprites/black-white/normal/rattata.png'),
