    (29,'Nidoran ♀',55,47,52,'Poison','NA','Poison Point','Rivalry','Hustle','7.0 kG','Blue','F (100%)','NA','It is related to the Nidoran♂ line, and can produce Eggs that contain either Nidoran♀ or Nidoran♂. However, it is the only one of its line that can breed, as Nidorina and Nidoqueen are part of the Undiscovered Egg Group. Both Nidoran''s, Nidorina, Nidorino, Poipole, and Naganadel are known as the Poison Pin Pokémon.','https://img.pokemondb.net/sprites/black-white/normal/nidoran-f.png'),
