    (58,'Growlithe',55,70,45,'Fire','NA','Intimidate','Flash Fire','Justified','19.0 kG','Brown','M (75%)','NA','A brave and loyal dog Pokémon that will bark and bite to defend its territory from intruders. Growlithe are popular throughout the Pokémon world as both guard dogs and police dogs. They are based on the Ryukyuan Shisa and Japanese Komainu lion-dog statues.','https://img.pokemondb.net/sprites/black-white/normal/growlithe.png'),
